column2: SELECT one, two FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN M.psfMag_i BETWEEN # AND # THEN # END one, CASE WHEN MM.psfMag_i BETWEEN # AND # THEN # END two FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) as N INNER JOIN PhotoTag AS M on M.objID = N.objID, dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) as NN INNER JOIN PhotoTag AS MM on MM.objID = N.objID) PhotoTag
